><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/655a1d6290da8d56174109bea0667e04-kix.79xrw79ii4sm-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/655a1d6290da8d56174109bea0667e04-kix.79xrw79ii4sm-jpg.webp 650w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/655a1d6290da8d56174109bea0667e04-kix.79xrw79ii4sm-300x158.webp 300w" width="650" height="342" /></a></p><p>招募期限：未知（仅通过初选者，将在复选后告知信息）</p><p> VTuber项目“ <a href="https://twitter.com/VhighOfficial" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Vhigh!</a> ”的第二次VTuber试镜已经开始。</p><p>通过将 VTuber 的活动从中心化转变为去中心化，Vhigh! 将构建一个基础设施，让 VTuber 感受到更多的自由和个性。我们的目标是提供元宇宙中虚拟活动所需的高质量虚拟形象和社区，并从Vhigh!中创造出大量的VTuber。</p><p>接受条件包括对自己的歌唱能力有信心的人、会说英语和韩语的人、有直播等活动经验的人、每周能直播5次以上的人。据透露，100%利润将被返还。</p><p>单击<a href="https://audition.vhigh.tokyo/jp" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此处</a>申请试镜。</p><p> （参考）<a href="https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000000013.000109879.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">HIGHBALL PTE. LTD 新闻稿</a></p><h2 id="link2">《纳纳哈皮》</h2><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/655a1d6290da8d56174109bea0667e04-kix.xs3yiz6x1d8h-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/655a1d6290da8d56174109bea0667e04-kix.xs3yiz6x1d8h-1024x512.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/655a1d6290da8d56174109bea0667e04-kix.xs3yiz6x1d8h-1024x512.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/655a1d6290da8d56174109bea0667e04-kix.xs3yiz6x1d8h-300x150.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/655a1d6290da8d56174109bea0667e04-kix.xs3yiz6x1d8h-768x384.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/655a1d6290da8d56174109bea0667e04-kix.xs3yiz6x1d8h-1536x768.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/655a1d6290da8d56174109bea0667e04-kix.xs3yiz6x1d8h-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="512"